  m_text: 'The group holding the citizens hostage within the dome are claiming to
    be resentful of our country''s governments ways of living and treating others,
    wishing to raise them into a better life. The dome structure was near completion
    at the time of the seizing, and as such it is likely properly inhabital for the
    residents.

    Currently, we have yet to seen any response from our government,
    and are awaiting one as such.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ab72a9c75c8230a4b9c3ea02b05222c8, type: 2}
